Package: gamCopula
Type: Package
Title: Generalized additive models for bivariate conditional dependence
    structures and Vine copulas
Version: 0.0-1
Date: 2015-06-17
Author: Thibault Vatter
Maintainer: Thibault Vatter <thibault.vatter@gmail.com>
Depends:
    R (>= 3.0.2)
Imports:
    VineCopula,
    mgcv,
    MASS,
    gsl,
    methods,
    copula,
    igraph,
    parallel
Description: This package implements various inference and simulation tools to
    apply generalized additive models to bivariate dependence structures and
    vine copulas.
